(serves 2)\
2 6-ounce (fresh) halibut fillets\uc0\u8232 1 tablespoon extra virgin olive oil\u8232 1 tablespoon plus 1 tablespoon unsalted butter, divided\u8232 3 cloves garlic, chopped\u8232 1/2 cup dry white wine\u8232 2 tablespoons capers\u8232 1 tablespoon fresh italian parsley, chopped\u8232 1/2 fresh lemon (zest and juice)\u8232 Kosher salt and freshly ground black pepper to taste\
3/4 pound fresh asparagus\
